    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s been well-loved and consistently maintained, so it\u2019s still running beautifully and ready for many more adventures with a new owner. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, smooth-driving car that still looks great in the driveway, this is definitely the one for you! I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 32000.0,
