      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, complete with its signature six independent throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring a visceral, analog connection to the tarmac. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a recent rod bearing service. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, maintaining the chassis' legendary balance and turn-in precision. While the exterior displays minor stone chips and patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are synchronized for peak performance. A true enthusiast's specimen that prioritizes drivetrain integrity and kinetic feedback.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
