    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-maintained daily driver that has been treated with consistent care. The exterior finish retains a brilliant shine, with only a few minor stone chips on the front fascia that are typical of highway use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin remains in excellent shape; the upholstery is free of tears, the carpets have been protected by floor mats, and all interior electronics\u2014including the premium audio system and dual-zone climate control\u2014function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, backed by a comprehensive service history that includes recent oil changes and a cooling system flush. The transmission shifts smoothly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. With a fresh set of tires and a recent professional detailing, this car is mechanically sound and aesthetically pleasing, offering a reliable and comfortable driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
