      "description": "Available for the serious driver: a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and remains thermally efficient under load. The double VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing across the rev range. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential, providing classic rear-drive dynamics. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary structural concern. While the finish reflects its status as a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical synchronization and suspension kinematics remain sharp. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing replacement, making this a turn-key performance machine for the analog purist.",
